  "name": "Improved Aiming",
  "type": "ability",
  "img": "icons/skills/targeting/crosshair-pointed-orange.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": "<p>Increases Hit chance by +10% for the next attack. The action may be repeated to stack the bonus, up to a maximum of +40%. A target can be aimed at any distance. If the attacker has four Aiming stacks on a target, they gain Armor Penetration +10. (Doctrine II – A hit reduces Aiming by only one level; a Critical Hit preserves all Aiming stacks.)</p>",
